  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "YOU DON'T JUST PLAY IT... YOU LIVE IT\nHe spins a web, swings across the sky and lands with a somersault onto the Daily Bugle building. Who is this masked hero? It's you! Fight, jump and web-sling as Spider-Man as you take on a legion of sinister villains.\n\nThe city is depending on you. Start swinging...",
